ol linking job seekers to goodpaying careers in new york’s financial services industry view all news our stories chase and current powered by ge collaborate to cut energy use in branches across the us  branches installing new energy management systems read the story  about chase and current powered by ge collaborate to cut energy use in branches across the us what can high school students learn from jamie dimon a qa session with the fellowship initiative los angeles read the story  about what can high school students learn from jamie dimon the sun breaks through thoughts from a tfi fellow moving past tragedy and toward hope read the story  about the sun breaks through thoughts from a tfi fellow view all stories new orleans service corps through our service corps program our international expertise is helping nonprofit partners grow read the story insights coming out in corporate america   by joe evangelisti how my gender transition made me a more valuable employee   by kathryn winters ask this simple question at work how are you   by stacey friedman coming out as lgbt isnt a onetime act   by allison steinberg should companies lead the lgbt equality revolution   by ken janssens and selisse berry view all insights video gallery in times of drought a safe and sustainable water supply jp morgan’s public finance team enables construction of western hemisphere’s largest desalination plant watch the video in times of drought a safe and sustainable water supply pushup challenge for a good cause employees across the company participated in the  pushups challenge in support of our commitment in hiring and retaining veterans watch the video on pushup challenge for a good cause this mom isnt taking baby steps our reentry program helps women who have taken a career break return to the workforce watch the video about our reentry program helps women who have taken a career break return to the workforce how can entrepreneurs get the start they need norwood clark cofounder of uncle 